  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll tell you in a moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the things that the farmers needed and the farmers had the food, the chickens, the wheat, the flour, the vegetables, that we needed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there would be market days when all the farmers would come to town and they would set up their wagons in a circle, all around that large square that I mentioned, near the shops and near the church and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jews would also set up shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there would be bartering, very little money exchanged, just one chicken for a pair of shoes or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is how it went on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And normally it would be a happy day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But every now and then, the farmers would start drinking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before you know it, one would say, well, let's have a little fun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they would say, well, let's beat up a few Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So suddenly they would start a pogrom, which was simply a disorganized, violent outrage, where women would be raped, houses would be burned, people would be killed, and it would be total chaos for the rest of the day, until things would quiet down, lives would be rebuilt again, and started all over again.",
      "word_count": 54
    }
  ],
